Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on developing an object recognition system and optimizing image encoding rate and neural network size for better performance. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper discusses the use of neural networks for object recognition. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing an intelligent system for object recognition. 
4. cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possible category as the paper discusses edge-assisted computing for optimizing system performance. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also a possible category as the paper deals with optimizing transmission delay in the system.
